{"tid":1722512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想成為專業sucker，應調較好生理時鍾","createTime":"2019-11-15T02:13:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T02:13:09.000Z","uid":278465,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4cfdbbaa0c65da8e5d0cb92a6d75ee24bd096139","tid":1722512,"uid":278465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:13:09.000Z","msg":"大家都知香港人平時幾夜訓架啦。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家仲係平時咁夜訓，再朝早6點左右起身，一兩日或者頂得順，但係再過多幾日，就真係攰到仆低。（自己就係好例子，依家趴左喺到打呢篇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n再加上啲打工仔唔係蠢嫁，好多都好早好早起身搭頭班車，遲到去suck功效不大。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以如果想成為專業sucker，唔該早啲訓，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">每日夜晚11點前好訓喇</span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n認同請正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔認同請負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}